args.title: Minor: Add more contemporary non-fiction recommendations
args.comment_body:
First of all, thank you for the excellent work on this repository—the curation and structure are both outstanding and very helpful for readers.

One small suggestion: it might be valuable to expand the list to include more contemporary non-fiction works (from roughly the last 10–15 years), especially in areas like:

- Technology and society
- Climate and environmental writing
- Global politics and economics
- Memoir and narrative non-fiction from underrepresented voices

This could help keep the list feeling fresh and relevant for newer readers while preserving the strong literary focus it already has.

If you think this fits the project’s scope, I’d be happy to help propose specific titles/categories in a follow-up PR or discussion. Thanks again for maintaining such a high-quality resource!
